nncBellcoreGR820Ds1IntervalIndex.name: nncBellcoreGR820Ds1IntervalIndex
nncBellcoreGR820Ds1IntervalIndex.description: A number between 1 and 96, which identifies the interval for which the set of statistics in this entry was collected. The interval identified by 1 is the most recently completed 15 minute interval, and the interval identified by 96 is the least recently completed 15 minute interval (assuming that all 96 inetrvals are valid).
